# Ghidra Assistant
Contains lots of bugs!

## Setup
```bash
pip install build
```

## Building
To build the GA
```bash
pip install build
python3 -m build
```

Next you can install the GA into your venv by:

```
source venv/bin/activate
python3 -m pip install dist/ghidra_assistant-0.0.1-py3-none-any.whl
```
